#. Tag: title
#: reference.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Menu"
msgstr "Menyn Visa"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Transaction Detail</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Visa</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Visa transaktionsinformation</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows transaction details in the <link linkend=\"details.ledgers\">Ledgers</"
"link> View. With this option turned on, all lines of the transaction will be "
"shown. When it is turned off, only one line will be shown."
msgstr ""
"Visar transaktionsinformation i vyn <link linkend=\"details.ledgers"
"\">Huvudbok</link>. Med alternativet aktiverat visas alla rader i "
"transaktionen. När det är inaktiverat visas endast en rad."

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you only want to see details for the currently selected transaction, but "
"only one line for the others, you can turn on the <link linkend=\"details."
"settings.register.lens\">Ledger Lens</link>."
msgstr ""
"Om du bara vill se information för transaktionen som för närvarande är "
"markerad, men bara en rad för de övriga, kan du aktivera <link linkend="
"\"details.settings.register.lens\">huvudbokens lins</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
